
### IV-S1: Receive Shipment (Success) # Logic: Auto-finds available bin and updates occupancy

POST {{baseUrlForInventory}}/receive
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "productId": "valid-product-uuid",
    "quantity": 25
}

### IV-F1: Insufficient Storage (Expected: 400) # Logic: Throws InsufficientStorageException if quantity > available space

POST {{baseUrlForInventory}}/receive
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "productId": "valid-product-uuid",
    "quantity": 999999
}